&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Band 4 Project Support Officer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Band 4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Digital Implementation Team has a vacancy for a Project Support Officer to work within the Team and assist in digitisation of the LTHT, helping deliver new technology and processes in the clinical environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is an opportunity for a suitably qualified and motivated &lt;strong&gt;Project Support Officer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; to join our team. The ideal candidate will have excellent organisational and communication skills, an ability to use their own initiative and to working to stringent deadlines, and will ideally have experience of working in a structured project environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please note that although the majority of the role will follow standard office hours some shift working will be required to support implementations in a clinical environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
